程序包 org.cloudbus.cloudsim.core

类 CloudInformationService

java.lang.Object
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.core.SimEntity
org.cloudbus.cloudsim.core.CloudInformationService
所有已实现的接口:
java.lang.Cloneable
public class CloudInformationService
extends SimEntity
A Cloud Information Service (CIS) is an entity that provides cloud resource registration, indexing and discovery services. The Cloud hostList tell their readiness to process Cloudlets by registering themselves with this entity. Other entities such as the resource broker can contact this class for resource discovery service, which returns a list of registered resource IDs. In summary, it acts like a yellow page service. This class will be created by CloudSim upon initialisation of the simulation. Hence, do not need to worry about creating an object of this class.
从以下版本开始:
CloudSim Toolkit 1.0
